# Config file encoding (UTF-8)

## Applies to

- vercel.json
- .github/**/*.yml / .github/**/*.yaml

## Required

UTF-8 without BOM. UTF-16 breaks Vercel (Invalid vercel.json) and GitHub YAML parsing.

## Forbidden on Windows

- PowerShell > / >> redirection
- Out-File / Set-Content without UTF-8 no BOM

## Safe writes

- Cursor / VS Code Save with Encoding UTF-8
- Node fs.writeFileSync(path, content, "utf8")
- PowerShell: [System.IO.File]::WriteAllText with UTF8Encoding false

## CI

.github/scripts/check-config-encoding.mjs runs in security-audit workflow.
